6/apple-amazon-prime-day-deal-sale-airpods-october" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24264786/apple-amazon-prime-day-deal-sale-airpods-october</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T18:49:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T18:49:03-04:00</updated><title>巴西的 X 禁令即将结束：所有最新消息</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;X 徽标的矢量拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BbT49Ndk9DNxhn4yM1ZQldvuXf0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73555180/STK160_X_TWITTER__C.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;最高法院法官亚历山大·德·莫赖斯 (Alexandre de Moraes) 在 X 公司遵守法院命令并缴纳罚款后，下令该国电信机构解封该公司。&lt;/p>; &lt; p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/30/24232573/brazil-x-twitter-ban-elon-musk&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/30/24232573/brazil-x-twitter-ban-elon-musk" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/30/24232573/brazil-x-twitter-ban-elon-musk</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>杰·彼得斯</name><name>亚历克斯·克兰兹</name><name>劳拉·马丁斯</name><name>艾玛·罗斯</name><name>莎拉·郑</name><name>理查德·劳勒</name><name>佐藤米娅</name><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name><name>托马斯·瑞克</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T18:31:02-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T18:31:02-04:00</updated><title>我们发现的最佳 Prime Day 智能家居优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/vLBiVUpxLoinHV1IJaNJVck6xDU=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639778 /247023_Echo_Hub_JTuohy_0003.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊的 Echo Hub 智能家居控制面板是在 Prime Big Deal Days 期间享受折扣的众多智能家居小工具之一。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;fm1O1l&quot;>;亚马逊的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24244180/amazon- october-prime-day-big-deal-days-fall-dates-2024&quot;>;Prime Big Deal Days&lt;/a>; 今天开始，一如既往，这是购买优质智能家居设备的绝佳时机。我搜索了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22954554/best-video-doorbell-camera&quot;>;视频门铃&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/22997597/best-robot-vacuum-cleaner&quot;>;扫地机器人&lt;/a>;、智能灯、智能扬声器等，收集了一些吸引我眼球的最便宜的商品。查看 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024 中所有优惠的完整列表”>;我们的主要帖子&lt;/a>;，并继续阅读智能家居优惠。促销持续到 10 月 9 日。&lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;uxfyp2&quot;>;智能扬声器和智能显示器&lt;/h2>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;7j5bey&quot;>;&lt;strong>;Echo Hub &lt;/strong>;是看到 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Echo-TP-Link-Tapo-Smart-Color/dp/B0DF15Y71Q?tag=theverge02-20&amp;amp;ascsubtag=__vg1008awD__24026509__L5Eboz________________https://www. theverge.com/&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;125 美元，低于 180 美元&lt;/a>;。这是亚马逊首款真正的智能家居控制器，是一款设计用于安装在墙上或放在桌子上的平板。它非常适合快速访问智能家居设备，如灯、锁、相机和音乐，并且可以兼作...&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/10/8/24264721/amazon-prime-day-best-smart-home-deals-sale-october-robot-vacuum&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24264721/amazon-prime-day-best-smart-home-deals-sale-october-robot-vacuum" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24264721/amazon-prime-day-best-smart-home-deals-sale-october-robot-vacuum</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T18:27:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T18:27:54-04:00</updated><title>白宫开始在 Reddit 上发帖谈论飓风米尔顿</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;用户whitehouse的reddit帐户页面&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/f51hwCpmKAq9ojIe-qCbo6TR9ts=/0x0:2263x1509/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73640883/Screenshot_2024_10_08_at_5.09.48_PM.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;该帐户上最早的帖子是拜登听取飓风简报的照片。&lt;/em>; |屏幕截图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;pMyqbZ&quot;>;Reddit 并不是您第一个看到来自联邦政府的官方声明和新闻的地方，但今天，白宫是在网站上发帖。您经常会看到员工在 Instagram 和 X 等社交媒体平台上发帖，宣布更新并吸引更多受众，所以这感觉很新鲜。拜登政府的“whitehouse”帐户在 r/NorthCarolina 和 r/Georgia 子版块&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/user/whitehouse/&quot;>;有新帖子&lt;/a>;，讨论联邦政府的应对措施飓风海伦和飓风米尔顿。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5dAW2k&quot;>;“是的，确实是我们！”白宫的账户在其中一条线索中说道。通常，这并不是一种完全令人信服的证明您身份的方式，但 Reddit 的 Gina Antonini 在一封电子邮件中告诉 &lt;em>;The Verge&lt;/em>; 这确实是一个合法帐户。安东尼尼...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265598/white-house-official-reddit-account-posting-hurricane&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265598/white-house-official-reddit-account-posting-hurricane" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265598/white-house-official-reddit-account-posting-hurricane</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T18:27:24-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T18:27:24-04:00</updated><title>巴西在一个月的禁令后允许 X 回归</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;X 徽标的矢量拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/PqpLiY8HBRa5XaBdLtbPJ4UOmaw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73640881/STK160_X_TWITTER_2__D.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;y1hjr4&quot;>;周二，巴西最高法院法官 Alexandre de Moraes &lt;a href=&quot;https://noticias.stf.jus.br/ postsnoticias/stf-autoriza-o-retorno-imediato-do-xe-determina-que-anatel-adote-providencias-para-a-retomada-do-servico/&quot;>;命令&lt;/a>;该国电信机构 Anatel 解除封锁X 在 24 小时内写道，它已满足“立即恢复活动所需的所有要求”。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;cVAkD7&quot;>;但是，这并不意味着应用程序会立即恢复服务。正如&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.poder360.com.br/poder-justica/alexandre-de-moraes-manda-desbloquear-ox-no-brasil/&quot;>;巴西分店&lt;em>;Poder360&lt; /em>;&lt;/a>;，Anatel 仍需要通知巴西 20,000 家不同的互联网服务提供商取消限制，具体情况会因他们使用的系统而异。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3n4LgN&quot;>;在 &lt;a href= 之前“https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/16/24131775/x-reverses-course-on-brazil&quot;>;8 月份向“法庭决定屏蔽巴西某些受欢迎的帐户”屈服，该公司已撤回其在该国的法定代表人，从而引发了禁令。然后，德莫赖斯法官&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/30/24231286/x-brazil-ban-elon-musk-legal-representative&quot;>;发布了禁令&lt;/a>;八月...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265606/x-twitter-unbanned-brazil-supreme-court&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265606/x-twitter-unbanned-brazil-supreme-court" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265606/x-twitter-unbanned-brazil-supreme-court</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T17:00:45-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T17:00:45-04:00</updated><title>不到 50 美元即可获得最佳 10 月 Prime Day 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;位于床头柜上的 Echo Spot 的照片。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nL1d_zBLRFdJqWxJp_t31Vr4D1g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639696/247196_Echo_Spot_Review_8A0A1 511_CVirginia.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊为其许多智能扬声器（包括新的 Echo Spot）提供免费的智能彩色灯泡。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;iZ4p4h&quot;>;亚马逊再次以 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge&quot; 为幌子举办第二个 Prime Day .com/2024/9/17/24244180/amazon-october-prime-day-big-deal-days-fall-dates-2024&quot;>;Prime Big Deal Days&lt;/a>;，持续到明天 10 月 9 日。虽然命名惯例可能很糟糕，但销售却并非如此。事实上，我们最喜欢的许多小工具和商品现在都在享受显着的折扣，我们在更大的综述中强调了这一点&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon -prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024&quot;>;黄金日最佳优惠&lt;/a>;。然而，如果您想控制预算，您可以在这里找到我们 50 美元以下的首选。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;TUx507&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;100 美元以下可获得的最佳 10 月 Prime Day 优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24264356/amazon-prime-day-best- Cheap-tech-deals-under-100-october-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何在亚马逊秋季 Prime Day 促销期间找到最优惠的价格&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /21502865/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以在我们最喜欢的一些小工具上获得的最佳 Prime Day 优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div >; &lt;p id=&quot;1dZhWj&quot;>;下面，我们精选了一些我们可以亲自担保的低于 50 美元的商品。当然，它们包括许多亚马逊自己的设备，包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/all-new-amazon-fire-tv-stick-4k-max/dp/B0BP9SNVH9?tag=theverge02 -20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fire TV Stick 4K Max&lt;/a>;，最新&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Echo-Spot-TP-Link -Smart-Color/dp/B0DF15V76B?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Spot&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com /Amazon-smart-plug-works-with-Alexa/dp/B089DR29T6?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊便宜的智能插头&lt;/a>;。非亚马逊上也有很多值得注意的交易...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech- Deals-under-50-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry></feed>